{"tid":856362,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【施政後成交】大興花園2期劈足「1球」僅售450萬","createTime":"2018-10-10T14:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T23:36:04.000Z","uid":174649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"219bde6f9b5ea7762d4d5dc5092a63a83e813c77","tid":856362,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181010/large/1539179641_c8bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181010%2Flarge%2F1539179641_c8bf.jpg&h=e4d043e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施政報告後屯門錄第一宗劈價。<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產胡志偉表示，屯門大興花園2期錄減價成交，3座中層H室，實用面積419方呎，上月叫價550萬元放盤，早兩星期已經有買家還價470萬元，但當時業主觀望市場變化放棄，及後市場反應冷淡，直至今天施政報告公佈，即晚累減100萬至450萬元終沽出，呎價10,740元。<br />\n<br />\n大興花園2期同面積單位高位成交，為9座高層H室，今年6月造價535萬元，呎價12,768元。是次造價重返年初水平。"},{"pid":"7aded1dad3c37d0844768d2d9ae67e0d8adab2a5","tid":856362,"uid":26451,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ee23cfac3d3f9e50ffaf5311339417ec719e6cd","tid":856362,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"屯門不如住牛棚。唔計"},{"pid":"801462155f107fd3357a6d50117733fb26a17c45","tid":856362,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾唔計"},{"pid":"aef5fc96c94ad56e87cff876df2fe940860ddae9","tid":856362,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲西樓早十年根本無買<br />\n<br />\n仲要四百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e4219211c323c288fcca6fdf43e311279741a0","tid":856362,"uid":28524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T20:43:25.000Z","msg":"十年前150萬，劈極都仲有得賺"},{"pid":"48fb8